sequenceDiagram
  actor Admin
  participant UI as "Web UI"
  participant Server as "API Server"
  participant DB as "Database"
  participant Email as "Email Service"
  actor User
  Admin->>UI: Configure & launch campaign
  UI->>Server: POST /api/campaigns
  Server->>DB: Get target users
  Server->>Email: Queue emails
  Email-->>User: Deliver simulated phishing
  User->>Server: Click tracking endpoint
  Server->>DB: Log click event
  Server-->>User: Redirect to landing page
